Text: True Quote AccessThank you for your interest in Truequotecom You can access our webenabled trading platform by going to wwwtruequotecom using your Internet Explorer or higher Once you hit our home page find the LOGIN tab Here is your password information USER ID joestep PASSWORD seminoles You may change your password anytime you like for increased security If you have difficulty ever logging into the system please contact Customer Service at Im also including the links below to help better explain Truequotes new functionality infotechhtm Tech Page outlining system requirements infofaqsethtm Frequently Asked Questions Attached below you will find a printable users guide to help you navigate the platform Please feel free to contact Client Services at at any time or you can reach me directly at Thank you Darci Gustafson Darci Gustafson Customer Service Representative Picture truequote users guide doc
